Description: Sherd of lip of East Greek pottery trefoil oenochoe; light ridge below lip; micaceous clay; wholly glazed, fired red-brown; inscription on outside.
Findspot: Excavated/Findspot: Sanctuary of Apollo (Naukratis), temenos (said to be)
